4121. 
TY  - JOUR
DB  - Embase
AN  - 613764691
T1  - Treatment of polycystic ovarian syndrome in primary care
A1  - Graham A.
A1  - Hamoda H. 
Y1  - 2016//
N2  - Polycystic ovarian syndrome (PCOS) is a common and complex syndrome that presents with a wide spectrum of clinical symptoms and is also associated with several other serious conditions. This article reviews the recommended management of PCOS and its associated symptoms in primary care and discusses when referral is necessary.Copyright © 2016 Wiley Interface Ltd
